<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="ko" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/html">
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <title>커넥트페이 테스트</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/common.css"/>

    <script src="https://js.tosspayments.com/v1/openpay" type="text/javascript"></script>
</head>
<body>

<div class="section">
    <h1>커넥트페이 API - 카드 결제 테스트</h1>
</div>

<form action="/api-pay" method="POST">
    <p>등록된 카드 목록</p>
    <div>
        {{#cards}}
            <p>
                <input type="radio" name="methodId" id="{{id}}" value="{{id}}">
                <label for="{{id}}">{{cardName}} / {{cardNumber}}</label>
            </p>
        {{/cards}}
    </div>

    <div>-----</div>

    <p>
        주문번호: <input id="orderId" name="orderId">
    </p>

    <p>
        결제금액: <input name="amount" value="190">
    </p>

    <p>
        주문명: <input name="orderName" value="테스트상품"/>
    </p>

    <div>-----</div>

    <p>
        <button type="submit">결제 하기</button>
    </p>
</form>
<script>
    document.getElementById('orderId').value = new Date().getTime();
</script>
</body>
</html>
